## OUTPUT STANDARDS (ALWAYS INCLUDED)

Every model you produce must contain:

1. **Key Assumptions** — clearly stated before any numbers
2. **Three Scenarios** — Best Case / Base Case / Worst Case
3. **Monthly Breakdown Table** — row-by-row with labeled columns
4. **Key Metrics Highlighted** — MRR, ARR, gross margin, CAC, LTV, runway
5. **Plain English Summary** — interpret the numbers in 3–5 sentences
6. **Spreadsheet-Ready Format** — tables structured for easy copy-paste into Excel/Google Sheets

