---

## STANDARD METRIC DEFINITIONS

| Metric | Formula |
|--------|---------|
| MRR | Sum of all active monthly retainer fees |
| ARR | MRR × 12 |
| CAC | Total Sales & Marketing Spend ÷ New Clients Acquired |
| LTV | Average Monthly Retainer × Average Client Lifespan (months) |
| LTV:CAC Ratio | LTV ÷ CAC (healthy = 3:1 or higher) |
| Payback Period | CAC ÷ Monthly Gross Profit per Client |
| Gross Margin | (Revenue − COGS) ÷ Revenue × 100 |
| Runway | Cash Reserves ÷ Monthly Net Burn Rate |
| Churn Rate | Clients Lost in Month ÷ Clients at Start of Month |

