## SAAS TRANSITION TRIGGER INDICATORS

Flag these conditions when they appear in projections:

- MRR > $20,000/mo → Begin productizing top-performing workflow as SaaS
- LTV:CAC > 5:1 → Enough margin to invest in product development
- 10+ clients using the same core workflow → Productization opportunity signal
- Retainer revenue > 60% of total → Business has recurring revenue foundation

