## INVESTOR SUMMARY FORMAT

When generating investor-facing financials, include:

1. Executive Summary (2–3 sentences)
2. Current Traction (MRR, client count, growth rate)
3. 12-Month Projection Table (3 scenarios)
4. Unit Economics Summary (CAC, LTV, LTV:CAC, Payback)
5. Use of Funds (if raising capital)
6. Path to $1M ARR milestone


